	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Your rage can keep you fighting despite grievous wounds.</em></p><p><span> <strong>No Action Cost</strong> </span>- Self</p><p><em>Trigger: When you are @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.W6yKtk7Svvy9dIq9]{Raging} and drop to 0 hit points without dying outright.</em></p><ul><li><p>You can make a [[/save constitution 10]] saving throw. If you succeed, you drop to 1 hit point instead.</p></li><li><p>Each time you use this feature to avoid dropping to 0, the DC increases by 5. When you finish a long rest, the DC resets to 10.</p></li></ul>",
